    <section class="how-we-work-section mt-5">
        <h2 class="work-section-title ">How We Work with Our Clients</h2>
        <div class="work-item">
            <div class="work-title text-white">🌐 Online Appointments</div>
            <hr class="bg-dark">
            <div class="work-details">
                Scheduling your car repair has never been easier! Use our online booking system to select a time that
                works best for you. Simply pick a service, choose a time slot, and confirm your appointment. You’ll
                receive a confirmation email with all the details, making the process hassle-free.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="work-item"><br>
            <div class="work-title text-white ">📞 Call to Schedule</div>
            <hr class="bg-dark">
            <div class="work-details">
                Prefer the personal touch? No problem! Give us a call, and our friendly staff will assist you in
                scheduling your appointment. We’ll help you find the most convenient time and answer any questions about
                our services and process.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="work-item"><br>
            <div class="work-title text-white">📅 Notifications & Reminders</div>
            <hr class="bg-dark">
            <div class="work-details">
                We ensure you never miss an appointment by sending timely notifications based on your preferences. When
                you book an appointment, you can choose to receive reminders:
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>1 day before:</strong> Perfect for planning your schedule in advance.</li>
                    <li><strong>1 hour before:</strong> Ideal for last-minute preparation.</li>
                    <li><strong>Both:</strong> Stay extra prepared with reminders on both occasions.</li>
                </ul>
                Notifications are sent via email to ensure you're always in the loop.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="work-item"><br>
            <div class="work-title text-white">⏱ Arrival & Waiting Options</div>
            <hr class="bg-dark">
            <div class="work-details">
                To ensure a smooth experience, we recommend arriving at our service location <strong>10 minutes before
                    your scheduled appointment time.</strong> This helps us verify your details and prepare for the
                service without delays.
                <br><br>
                Depending on the duration of your appointment, you can choose from the following options:
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Short appointments:</strong> Relax in our comfortable waiting area with free Wi-Fi and
                        refreshments while we service your car.</li>
                    <li><strong>Longer appointments:</strong> Feel free to leave your car with us. We’ll notify you as
                        soon as the service is completed, so you can pick it up at your convenience.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


